## 🚀 COMANDOS

### Desenvolvimento

```bash
pip install -e ".[all,dev]"   # Instalar
cortex-api                    # API REST
cortex-mcp                    # MCP Server
pytest tests/ -v              # Testes
ruff check src/               # Lint
```

### Benchmark

```bash
./start_benchmark.sh --quick   # Rápido (~10 min)
./start_benchmark.sh --full    # Completo (~1 hora)
./analyze_results.sh           # Análise
```

